code: public boolean addExportException(ExportException e) {     return exceptions.add(e). }

@Override public void writeTo(StreamOutput out) throws IOException {     super.writeTo(out).     out.writeVInt(exceptions.size()).     for (ExportException e : exceptions) {         e.writeTo(out).     } }

@Override protected void metadataToXContent(XContentBuilder builder, Params params) throws IOException {     if (hasExportExceptions()) {         builder.startArray("exceptions").         for (ExportException exception : exceptions) {             builder.startObject().             exception.toXContent(builder, params).             builder.endObject().         }         builder.endArray().     } }
